,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:54:55.000Z","msg":"反正咩都入侵侵數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講仲以為美國係獨裁國家<br />\n啲州長州政府好似唔存在咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:57:17.000Z","msg":"依家真係便秘都係Trump問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:58:52.000Z","msg":"一定係因為佔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:13:25.000Z","msg":"左膠響twitter黎黎去去都係果句「It's Trump's America」<br />\n所以左膠先係美國藍絲"},{"pid":"90f95940a1c9e0846fb08e6c64f82ae5c4c73e57","tid":2203090,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60816e837c59143b55510cea1fadd346d080bd26","tid":2203090,"uid":259901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ec061414c5eae0b16c38c57ea3edb4ada7dddd0e","tid":2203090,"uid":34869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f690ee92a2413a1668c02bec816fab1768c7dc25","tid":2203090,"uid":259901,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:44:10.000Z","msg":"換個角度諗<br />\n黑暗小小<br />\n我係侵仔<br />\n還掂我做乜都好<br />\n你加州都係投拜燈<br />\n咁我做乜要理你哋先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:56:57.000Z","msg":"其實真係差唔多次次都係加州著火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:59:31.000Z","msg":"一次兩次可以話天災人禍冇法子<br />\n屌你老母年年都係你大火<br />\n係咪應該檢討下自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:14:18.000Z","msg":"左膠會檢討自己就唔係左膠"},{"pid":"fc5816b01d2c5b375a94864bd3bc944a196746e9","tid":2203090,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"992d67989251a2b79067f3d26eb94b35d6718f66","tid":2203090,"uid":152944,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"喺奧巴馬任內氣候好轉咗幾多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:17:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">臭黑馬政績系列</span></strong></span><br />\n2012年&mdash;&mdash; 當地時間2012年8月20日，美國加利福尼亞州格林維爾，山火繼續肆虐。加州北部偏遠地區18日因雷電引發山林大火，火勢20日逼近3座小鎮，數千戶人家受到山火威脅。近1900名消防員在火區從事滅火工作。在農村地區對山林大火進行評估的工作人員21日確定，50棟建築被燒毀。<br />\n<br />\n2013年&mdash;&mdash;2013年5月31日，美國加州卡斯泰克市附近，消防直升機正在參與撲滅山火。<br />\n2013年7月15日 美國加州河濱縣爆發森林大火 截止目前已燒毀20座建築 6輛汽車 沒有人員傷亡。<br />\n2013年8月17日，加州斯坦尼斯勞斯國家森林(Stanislaus National Forest)發生火災，並迅速蔓延至附近的優美勝地國家公園(Yosemite National Park)。這起大火被稱為「「環火(Rim Fire)」，因為它開始於斯坦尼斯勞斯國家森林內一個叫世界之環(Rim of the World)的景點。大火已燒焦了近<span class=\"red\">15萬</span>英畝土地，燒毀了23幢建築物，<span class=\"red\">成為加州1932年有記錄以來第13大火災</span><br />\n<br />\n2014年&mdash;&mdash;2014年9月，加州發生10多起山火，受災面積達297平方英里即<span class=\"red\">19萬平方英畝</span>(約770平方公里)。<br />\n<br />\n2015年&mdash;&mdash;當地時間2015年12月26日，美國加州文圖拉縣索利馬爾地區發生森林火災， 消防官員稱，大火燒毀了大約<span class=\"red\">1100英畝</span>（約合6677畝）的植被，當局被迫關閉了兩條主要的高速公路，並疏散居民。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>離任前都要燒多獲</strong><br />\n2016年&mdash;&mdash;據美國合眾社8月1日報道，加州大蘇爾附近的大火已經持續超過一周，過火面積達<span class=\"red\">4萬英畝</span>，相當於整箇舊金山市大。7月31日，有兩個社區被要求撤離，近70棟建築被大火摧毀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只計第二任期已經嬴到開項<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe9b27b830867bbdd6c2856956477125969ea520","tid":2203090,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc5816b01d2c5b375a94864bd3bc944a196746e9","tid":2203090,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"992d67989251a2b79067f3d26eb94b35d6718f66","tid":2203090,"uid":152944,"like":3,